(5, 2, 'Nature Inspired Earrings - Alex Monroe Designer Jewellery', 'nature-inspired-earrings-alex-monroe-designer-jewellery', '1778492593_2tZCVJu4u5.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '<h1>Earrings</h1>\r\n<div class=\"category-description\">\r\n<div data-content-type=\"row\" data-appearance=\"contained\" data-element=\"main\">\r\n<div data-enable-parallax=\"0\" data-parallax-speed=\"0.5\" data-background-images=\"{}\" data-background-type=\"image\" data-video-loop=\"true\" data-video-play-only-visible=\"true\" data-video-lazy-load=\"true\" data-video-fallback-src=\"\" data-element=\"inner\" data-pb-style=\"W68VWVV\">\r\n<div data-content-type=\"text\" data-appearance=\"default\" data-element=\"main\">\r\n<p>From everyday essentials to statement pieces for special occasions, our earring collections offer something for every style and moment. Perfect for gifting or indulging yourself, each piece is designed to be both versatile and timeless. Mix and match metals, explore our designs featuring ethically sourced gemstones and diamonds, and create the perfect pair of earrings that are uniquely yours.</p>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking for inspiration, browse our&nbsp;<a title=\"Shop our bestselling jewellery\" href=\"https://www.alexmonroe.com/bestsellers\">bestselling pieces</a> to find your next favourite earrings.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2026-05-11 03:43:13', '2026-05-11 03:43:13'),
(6, 2, 'Gold Earrings – Latest Designs for Men & Women | Tanishq', 'gold-earrings-latest-designs-for-men-women-tanishq', '1778492721_E2rrCoX8Un.jpg', 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '<h2 data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2a0e.pdp_revamp.product_detail.i1.3a9b23b5RbvdCv\">pecification:</h2>\r\n<p>Indulge in the luxurious comfort of this gold-plated jewellery ✨, featuring a smooth surface that is skin-friendly, allowing you to wear it effortlessly for extended periods.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted with meticulous attention, this piece not only enhances your existing jewellery collection but also ensures a lasting impression on those around you.</p>\r\n<p>Elevate your style with this affordable and exquisite gold-plated accessory 💎, making it a perfect gift for your loved ones.</p>\r\n<p>This modern jewellery is beautifully crafted in a special cut ✂️, allowing you to make a glamorous statement on any occasion.</p>\r\n<p>The glamorous and elegant design of this jewellery seamlessly complements both traditional and western attire, adding a touch of sophistication to your ensemble.</p>', '2026-05-11 03:45:21', '2026-05-11 03:45:21'),
